divs: sighting details4th of july, lower mannhatten n.y.c. about 7pm took a bunch of pictures,two hours before the fireworks and seen some odd shapes of saucer\disc one high and another very low. i took many frames of the same angle,i dont think it is reflection,because the others dont have a saucer shape in them, and in the higher frame photo there is an object miles up that has a saucer shape,the picture of the object that is the lower in the frame seems to have more height then a street light that is included in the picture,once again i have multiple photos in the same angles,but only two have objects in them.
